<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316 0%, #9ca3af 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .content { padding: 20px; background: #f9f9f9; }
      .footer { padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
      .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #f97316; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; }
      .info-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; }
      .info-table td { padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; }
      .info-table td:first-child { font-weight: bold; width: 40%; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Application Submitted Successfully</h1>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= @owner&.first_name || 'Applicant' %>,</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for submitting your company formation application. We have received your application and it is now being reviewed by our team.</p>
        
        <table class="info-table">
          <tr>
            <td>Application ID:</td>
            <td><%= @company.id.split('-').first.upcase %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Company Name (Primary):</td>
            <td><%= @company.name_options&.first || 'Pending' %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Free Zone:</td>
            <td><%= @company.free_zone %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Submitted At:</td>
            <td><%= @company.submitted_at&.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Status:</td>
            <td>Under Review</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        
        <h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Document Review:</strong> Our team will review your submitted documents (1-2 business days)</li>
          <li><strong>Name Approval:</strong> We'll check the availability of your chosen company names</li>
          <li><strong>Payment Request:</strong> Once approved, you'll receive a payment link</li>
          <li><strong>Company Formation:</strong> After payment, we'll proceed with the official registration</li>
          <li><strong>License Issuance:</strong> Your trade license will be issued within 5-7 business days</li>
        </ol>
        
        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
          <a href="http://localhost:3000/dashboard" class="button">View Application Status</a>
        </p>
        
        <p><strong>Need Help?</strong><br>
        If you have any questions about your application, please contact our support team at support@simplesetup.ae or call +971 4 123 4567.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© 2024 Simple Setup. All rights reserved.<br>
        Dubai, United Arab Emirates</p>
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
